result.name: Chaiwala

reviews.text:
We’ve been visiting this place ever since it has opened. Good food Good ambience and lovely staff. 
We ordered their tasting menu and the pictures are all that we were served 😁
Very friendly and helpful staff, food is not necessarily authentic Indian who said good food has to be authentic? As long as it’s yummy! Brunch is really good value.
Funky atmosphere. Good food. Seems like good date place. If you want to chat, best sit at bar because it's loud inside.

Was blown away by every thing in this place, the food, the staff and the decor. Just the space in general and the open kitchen... Crazy! Really delicious Indian food and I can't wait to come back and try everything else on the menu

The space is very nice and the menu is interesting. Prices were reasonable. I wanted to like the dishes but each fell short for me. The fish curry was thin and the flavors didn't pop. The naan fluffy like bread. The prawns were a bit tough and fishy. I'd go back, particularly for drinks, but I would think seek it out.
